左右大部份支那蝗日日煲冬瓜 諗下都頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n精神病果班好多住公屋<br />\n先前東張西望先報導有個婆婆專執垃圾返屋低<br />\n搞到勁臭<br />\n<br />\n搵HO投訴，但拉布唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf7efa76bbb89bf4ddeeb42ec296625f3835af6","tid":246522,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:13:54.000Z","msg":"其實已經供緊樓，即係男人佢自己一個都供得到，使撚女人幫手供咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbc05739eaf85094278bdc9fafb7e3183e8ec0e","tid":246522,"uid":77961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"供樓仲衰過無樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75343b663a59c96f0f0044b83f5455cf6d8ad8de","tid":246522,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"第三位<br />\n有車"},{"pid":"894c98b1d387ee0d090268139526e0e5a33dbe06","tid":246522,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>供樓仲衰過無樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n銀行借得錢比你供份糧都唔少野啦<br />\n篇文膠成咁係咪又係果D公屋仔寫"},{"pid":"e548129e3366a6938596ee8f7c48dd3f872b7c78","tid":246522,"uid":64409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:17:31.000Z","msg":"住公屋我當交多啲税 <br />\n利申：公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d3b5a2cb08e4b605c2705b068a6e64b4a6cd82","tid":246522,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"陪供樓係最慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4da45f4bac910d808bd832a6b36e2c52ea3ec21","tid":246522,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>供樓仲衰過無樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個有風險, 一個無.<br />\n<br />\n根本傻都識揀, 唔係公屋都唔駛有限制la.<br />\n大把公務員有得揀供樓津貼定公屋, 都係揀公屋多."},{"pid":"8e854b89ae2617340cea9d38a870f762c136f105","tid":246522,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"[quote][quote]屌 第2位都一樣冇女[/quote］<br />\n介唔介意po自己張相上黎討論下"},{"pid":"ca0cfa68c5fcb96f5f0756ae5123349eda633b05","tid":246522,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"公屋都無租緊樓個啲點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dd660d3bca2a93a8cfcce7f67b7a2eeb742835","tid":246522,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"1. 第六位同第七位究竟係乜撚野事<br />\n<br />\n住私樓唔好過公屋?<br />\n<br />\n2. 其實你唔想供無問題<br />\n我可以同你結婚<br />\n但層樓你唔使旨意有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 但公屋戶主一係死好彩排到，<br />\n一係死老豆老母而又無錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a94abbd43db46af7beb83cf7473e71013a210aa","tid":246522,"uid":70085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"排第尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e7efb2c51be63b02281b44df691688c22d25e2","tid":246522,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公屋都無租緊樓個啲點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該仲衰過同家人同住<br />\n除非好高收入，如果唔係份糧折左三四成衰過同父母住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba9c845abfc24216cd33992c16c5a2fc953a354","tid":246522,"